s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:3:\"url\";s:71:\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/VIRTUAL_GIFT_CARD_8.mp4\";s:6:\"length\";s:1:\"0\";s:4:\"type\";s:9:\"video/mp4\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Ausilia\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11613:\"<p>Christmas is coming and its the time of the year when our Gift Cards plugin becomes the most popular of the entire catalogue.</p>\n<p>After all, surveys show evidence: everyone loves gift cards, especially at Christmas time, and many consider our YITH Gift Cards plugin the most complete and versatile one. Maybe because weve put our hearts in it and have been constantly adding new handy features. Or maybe because of the 5-star support that we offer to customers who use the plugin in their shop.</p>\n<p>Anyway, <strong><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-gift-cards/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">YITH WooCommerce Gift Cards</a></strong> is aware of its own worth and has got a big head recently.</p>\n<p>It became ambitious and aimed to be even more beautiful, even smarter.</p>\n<p>Especially when it comes to design and usability.</p>\n<p>For the past two months weve locked it into a cocoon made of code and design and worked on it without interruption, to improve the admin panel usability, to make the gift card page modern and appealing and to add all the options that youve been asking us for during this time.</p>\n<p>We are proud of the final result and are eager to present all the new features of YITH Gift Cards 3.0 (and give some insight on the ones scheduled for version 3.1. Cause we never stop!)</p>\n<h2>A new usable and functional backend</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image4.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096638\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1438\" height=\"905\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image4.png 1438w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image4-300x189.png 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image4-1024x644.png 1024w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image4-768x483.png 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image4-261x164.png 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image4-311x196.png 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image4-363x228.png 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image4-270x170.png 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1438px) 100vw, 1438px\" /></a></p>\n<p>First of all, we started from the new design of our plugin framework and applied it to the whole backend, then we reorganised the collocation of the available options and cleared the code to improve the plugin performances.</p>\n<p>All the settings are now split into specific tabs, which makes the user interface much more usable.</p>\n<h2>The new interface of the Gift Card page</h2>\n<p>Lets be honest, the gift card page was somehow obsolete and had some usability issues as well.</p>\n<p>Redesigning it was a challenging task, but it was worth it. What do you think?</p>\n<div style=\"width: 1140px;\" class=\"wp-video\"><!--[if lt IE 9]><script>document.createElement(\'video\');</script><![endif]-->\n<video class=\"wp-video-shortcode\" id=\"video-1096634-1\" width=\"1140\" height=\"886\" loop=\"1\" autoplay=\"1\" preload=\"metadata\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"video/mp4\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/VIRTUAL_GIFT_CARD_8.mp4?_=1\" /><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/VIRTUAL_GIFT_CARD_8.mp4\">https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/VIRTUAL_GIFT_CARD_8.mp4</a></video></div>\n<p>    <div class=\"spacer\" style=\"height: 50px;\"></div>\n	<br />\nOn the left, you&#8217;ll find the gift card template that updates in real time and on the right you&#8217;ll find all the options to customize it (you can activate them one by one from the plugin settings):</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Pick one of the default images;</li>\n<li>Open the modal window with all images sorted by category;</li>\n<li>Upload a custom image or a picture;</li>\n<li>Choose the amount or enter your own custom amount;</li>\n<li>Pick a date from the calendar to deliver the gift card email;</li>\n<li>Add more than one recipient.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also the Gift this product option underwent surgery and this is what it looks like now:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image2-1.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096636\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image2-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1031\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image2-1.png 1200w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image2-1-300x258.png 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image2-1-1024x880.png 1024w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image2-1-768x660.png 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image2-1-261x224.png 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image2-1-311x267.png 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image2-1-363x312.png 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image2-1-270x232.png 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /></a></p>\n<p>In version 3.0 we&#8217;ve added an option (repeatedly requested by many of our customers) to allow <strong>using the gift card codes in the coupon box</strong> in Cart and Checkout: this will prevent any possible misunderstanding generated by using different fields for gift cards and coupon codes.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image7.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096641\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image7.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1438\" height=\"666\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image7.png 1438w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image7-300x139.png 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image7-1024x474.png 1024w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image7-768x356.png 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image7-261x121.png 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image7-311x144.png 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image7-363x168.png 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image7-270x125.png 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1438px) 100vw, 1438px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Version 3.0 is already available. Take advantage of the <a href=\"https://plugins.yithemes.com/yith-woocommerce-gift-cards/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>live demo</strong></a>to give it a try and see with your own eyes the revolution weve carried out <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/12.0.0-1/72x72/1f642.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n<p>Moreover, we will soon release <em><strong>version 3.1</strong></em>, where you will find:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Options to customize the gift card right in the modal window: simple mode or in steps.    <div class=\"spacer\" style=\"height: 15px;\"></div>\n	<br />\n<a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image5.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096639\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1438\" height=\"1242\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image5.png 1438w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image5-300x259.png 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image5-1024x884.png 1024w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image5-768x663.png 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image5-261x225.png 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image5-311x269.png 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image5-363x314.png 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image5-270x233.png 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1438px) 100vw, 1438px\" /></a></li>\n<li>An option to send the gift card also by SMS (and we will do our best to add also Whatsapp and Telegram options)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img class=\"size-full wp-image-1101713 aligncenter\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/deliverymode.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"787\" height=\"553\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/deliverymode.jpg 787w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/deliverymode-300x211.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/deliverymode-768x540.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/deliverymode-261x183.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/deliverymode-311x219.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/deliverymode-363x255.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/deliverymode-270x190.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 787px) 100vw, 787px\" /></p>\n<ul>\n<li>A shortcode for the Gift this product option to use this feature anywhere you like: in a widget in the product page sidebar, in shop page, inside a graphic banner and so on.<br />\n<a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image1-1.png\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-1096635 aligncenter\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image1-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1014\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image1-1.png 1200w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image1-1-300x254.png 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image1-1-1024x865.png 1024w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image1-1-768x649.png 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image1-1-261x221.png 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image1-1-311x263.png 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image1-1-363x307.png 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image1-1-270x228.png 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /></a></li>\n<li>An option to let users set up the gift card generated through Gift this product in a modal window;    <div class=\"spacer\" style=\"height: 50px;\"></div>\n	<a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image3-1.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096637\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image3-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1277\" height=\"1480\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image3-1.png 1277w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image3-1-259x300.png 259w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image3-1-884x1024.png 884w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image3-1-768x890.png 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image3-1-261x302.png 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image3-1-311x360.png 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image3-1-363x421.png 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/image3-1-270x313.png 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1277px) 100vw, 1277px\" /></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>    <div class=\"spacer\" style=\"height: 50px;\"></div>\n	<br />\nDo you want to learn more about it? Take a look at the plugin in the <a href=\"https://plugins.yithemes.com/yith-woocommerce-gift-cards/\">live demo</a>and make some tests: check the new plugin style or go through the <a href=\"https://docs.yithemes.com/yith-woocommerce-gift-cards/changelog/changelog-premium-version/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">full changelog</a> if you want to read the new changes of this update.</p>\n<p>If youve installed YITH Gift Cards plugin in your e-commerce store, you can update it to the new version and start with the new modern and intuitive interface right now.</p>\n<p>Whereas if you havent installed a Gift cards system yet, do it now! This is the best time to take remedial action and give your users one of the most useful and popular services at Christmas time.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:107:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/yit-news/not-just-an-update-a-brand-new-redesign-for-yith-gift-cards-plugin/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"4\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"A new login &amp; register plugin to reduce the cart abandonment rate\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:99:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/yit-news/a-new-login-register-plugin-to-reduce-the-cart-abandonment-rate/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:107:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/yit-news/a-new-login-register-plugin-to-reduce-the-cart-abandonment-rate/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 28 Nov 2019 12:27:23 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"YITH News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"https://yithemes.com/?p=1096612\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:339:\"We at YITH take statistics seriously, really. Especially when they are about e-commerce and conversions. So, you can imagine our disappointment when we discovered that 35% of e-customers abandon the cart and do not finalise the purchase because they are forced to create an account. People want to buy, but this process has to be [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Ausilia\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8140:\"<p><strong>We at YITH take statistics seriously, really.</strong></p>\n<p>Especially when they are about e-commerce and conversions.</p>\n<p>So, you can imagine our disappointment when we discovered that <a href=\"https://designadvisor.net/blog/shopping-cart-abandonment-stats/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">35% of e-customers abandon the cart</a> and do not finalise the purchase because they are forced to create an account.</p>\n<p>People want to buy, but this process has to be easy and quick. If they have to stop to fill out a form with an incredibly high number of fields, they will start thinking twice about the purchase. They will ask themselves if they really need that product, the dopamine value will drop down, and they will start getting a sense of guilt for their impulsive action.</p>\n<p>And then boom! Cart is abandoned. Thats just the way things go.</p>\n<p>Well, these statistics were tormenting us and we were wondering what we could have done to avoid it. First of all, what could we do for ourselves, for our own business? After all, YITH is an e-commerce shop. It goes without saying that the nightmare of cart abandonment is something that causes us great concern.</p>\n<p>Secondly, we were struggling to find a tool to contain the issue and that could be shared with our customers too.</p>\n<p>How could we simplify the login and registration process? Make it so easy that it would not annoy any customers during the purchase?</p>\n<p>And also: how could we reduce the frustration of those scatterbrained returning customers that found themselves bound to leave the checkout process and set up a new password for their account?</p>\n<p>The answer was as simple as that: we could, yes, but <em>only with a plugin</em>.</p>\n<p>We worked out a solution that could streamline this process, and for that, we took inspiration from big and sound e-commerce stores like Etsy and Amazon. We carried out a usability test, designed a smart interface in every single step and mapped the whole user journey: this took us to the release of the new plugin YITH Easy Login &amp; Register for WooCommerce.     <div class=\"spacer\" style=\"height: 15px;\"></div>\n	</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/easy_login.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1097093\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/easy_login.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1152\" height=\"324\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/easy_login.jpg 1152w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/easy_login-300x84.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/easy_login-1024x288.jpg 1024w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/easy_login-768x216.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/easy_login-1000x280.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/easy_login-261x73.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/easy_login-311x87.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/easy_login-363x102.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/easy_login-270x76.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1152px) 100vw, 1152px\" /></a>    <div class=\"spacer\" style=\"height: 15px;\"></div>\n	</p>\n<h3>What is it about?</h3>\n<p>It is a charming-designed modal window that allows your customers to log in or register during the checkout and to split the process into two simple steps with the aim of improving the usability and simplify things to the final user.</p>\n<h3>How does it work, practically?</h3>\n<p>Its easy. During the first step, the user will only have to enter an account name or an email address. As an alternative, they can log in with Facebook or Google, and this is an option that most customers do really appreciate.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1097306\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"836\" height=\"732\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-2.jpg 836w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-2-300x263.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-2-768x672.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-2-261x229.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-2-311x272.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-2-363x318.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-2-270x236.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 836px) 100vw, 836px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If the user has an existing account in your e-commerce, the next step will be to enter the password; if its a new account, they simply have to set a new password and proceed to the checkout. In both cases, the second step will ask them to enter a password, nothing else. Quick and easy.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1097298\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1666\" height=\"1412\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-1.jpg 1666w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-1-300x254.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-1-1024x868.jpg 1024w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-1-768x651.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-1-1536x1302.jpg 1536w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-1-261x221.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-1-311x264.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-1-363x308.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-1-270x229.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1666px) 100vw, 1666px\" /></a></p>\n<p>And what if the email is the right one but the customer forgot the password?</p>\n<p>No drama.</p>\n<p>With one click, they will receive a code in their email and use it to set up a new password, still from the same modal window, <strong>without leaving the checkout process, ever</strong>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-4.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1097319\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"634\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-4.png 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-4-300x190.png 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-4-768x487.png 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-4-261x165.png 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-4-311x197.png 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-4-363x230.png 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Senza-titolo-4-270x171.png 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Just one more click and they can finally pay. Its impossible to make it easier than this. Guaranteed!</p>\n<p>With YITH Easy Login &amp; Register you can activate a usable, modern and attractive interface and guarantee a fluid registration, login and password recovery process for your customers.</p>\n<p>All this during the checkout process to <strong>reduce the cart abandonment rate considerably</strong>, but theres still more: thanks to the CSS selectors, you will be able to use this modal window in other places in your e-commerce store. Just to give an example, you can show it also when the user clicks on the classic Login/register button in your website header.</p>\n<h3>Do you still have doubts?</h3>\n<p>Take a look at the <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-easy-login-register-for-woocommerce/\"><strong>product page</strong></a> or test the <a href=\"https://plugins.yithemes.com/yith-easy-login-register-popup-for-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>plugin demo</strong></a>!</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:104:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/yit-news/a-new-login-register-plugin-to-reduce-the-car